Small improvement for Warpcast mobile

- Multiple links will display in a more compact format

- No algo penalty for links, just making them take up less visual space, esp. on a small device

- Also more gracefully degrades handles when OpenGraph data doesn’t render

Reminder for channel hosts

Start a discussion with your current co-hosts about which account will own the channel onchain. We still have some time, but better to start early.

Expect developers to build smart contract infra for channel ownership that can be controlled by multiple people or even a DAO.

For those reaching out about partnering or powering a specific part of channels — the goal is to make the protocol primitive 1) simple 2) flexible.

The channel stack (i.e. "legos") will be a marketplace. If you're a developer with a good idea, you have the freedom to build it.

cast.text:
Decentralizing channels sequence

1. Next week — moving all channels over to the new model (Phase 1 in below doc)

2. Will monitor UX and make any adjustments 

3. End of May / early June — Phase 2 draft technical spec

text:
Is it just me, or does it feel like FarCon marked the top?

DAUs feels a LOT less than before. 

@pichi and I both agreed this week in general has been pretty weird. 

Vibes feel off.

Going on my third summer here. 

Summer is usually slower, people actually try to do vacations and family time. 

No matter your lat/long. Let’s see if this year is the same. 

Farcon signals, “summer is coming”.
